<treatmentCitation id="707B705BE234FFCC7330F8300767F85A" author="Lehtinen" box="[337,529,2015,2037]" page="54" pageId="4" pageNumber="447" year="1981">
<bibRefCitation id="954B2BBBE234FFCC7330F8300498F85A" author="Lehtinen" box="[337,494,2015,2037]" pageId="4" pageNumber="447" refString="Lehtinen, P. T. (1981) Spiders of the Oriental-Australian region. III. Tetrablemmidae, with a world revision. Acta Zoologica Fennica, 162, 1 - 151." type="journal article" year="1981">Lehtinen, 1981</bibRefCitation>
